 x^{4 p+2} + \frac{b_p}{\sin{\frac{d \pi}{2}}} x^{4-d + 4 p} ]  \\
&& a_p = \frac{  2^{-d}}{(2 p)! \Gamma
   \left(\frac{d}{4}+p\right)} 

